ACADEMIC INTEGRITY NOTICE FOR STUDENTS:

This framework is provided as a learning tool for MC3113 students. While you 
may freely use and modify this code:

1. Your controller implementation (my_controller_step.m) must be your own work
2. Sharing controller code with other students constitutes plagiarism
3. You may discuss concepts and algorithms, but not share implementation code
4. All submissions will be checked for similarity
5. Violations will be reported according to university academic integrity policies

By using this software for coursework, you agree to uphold these academic 
integrity standards.